<span id="freeTextContainer5540541480379171066">Another enjoyable read (or rather, listen) during biking to work. I really like this series! It a good adventure series, suitable for boys and girls (12+) and I&apos;m really happy there are so many more books :D I liked the humor and the plot, and oh my that ending!</span>
  <span id="freeText5540541480379171066" style="display:none">Another enjoyable read (or rather, listen) during biking to work. I really like this series! It a good adventure series, suitable for boys and girls (12+) and I'm really happy there are so many more books :D I liked the humor and the plot, and oh my that ending!</span>
