<li class='cover' id='bookCover_2146957'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2146957.Grip_of_the_Shadow_Plague"><img alt="Grip of the Shadow Plague (Fablehaven, #3)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388607686l/2146957._SX98_.jpg" />
