iekielny reaguje na &quot;kici, kici&quot;?\nCzy w tej rodzinie &quot;i żyli długo i szczęśliwie&quot; jest w ogóle możliwe bez małej katastrofy?\n\nDługo wyczekiwana książka o nietuzinkowym klanie Koźlaków, znanych z opowiadań w antologiach Dynia i jemioła, Harda Horda i Idiota skończony.\nW Zielonym Jarze nie zdołacie się nudzić. Narcyza Koźlak nigdy na to nie pozwoli.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"14643636211640401840\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'15_book_55281692\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"x7BuPY/8hT4R46tqoi9Ste7+RPB6dxRTd2uK+z92M7E9Ymjcf2alxn1rxaR2OZTop9ftuf7f/d1Qbw9ZaCmLVQ==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"55281692\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"15_book_55281692\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/144349.The_Burning_Bridge\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\n<span class=\'progressTrigger\'>Want to Read<\/span>\n<span class=\'progressIndicator\'>saving…<\/span>\n<\/button>\n<\/form>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class